com.pixelmed.dicom

Class DicomDictionary

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pixelmed.dicom.DicomDictionaryBase
      • com.pixelmed.dicom.DicomDictionary
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DicomDictionaryForMinimalPatientStudySeriesInstanceModel, DicomDictionaryForPatientStudySeriesConcatenationInstanceModel, DicomDictionaryForStudySeriesInstanceModel

    public class DicomDictionary
extends DicomDictionaryBase

    The DicomDictionary class is a complete standard dictionary of DICOM attributes and associated information.

    The accessor methods that an application would normally use are defined in the DicomDictionaryBase class.
